{
  "stem": "2581.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what I'm saying, you know, it's completely a different environment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Besides, it was a small town, where everyone knew everyone, from generation to generation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, we had the Maccabi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did all the sports, what is usually done in the sports club.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In our building, where we lived, was the Stern, which was more a political organization with sports.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stern means the-- stern is a star, which, in a way represents the symbol of the left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we belonged to Maccabi, which was a Zionist, supposedly non-political sports organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, Maccabi exists to this very day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's so happens that the instructor of this Maccabi had gone to Israel very early in the '30s, and he became the tsar of sport in Israel.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name is Schmuel Bialig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was the right hand to the mayor of Haifa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Five minutes ago I knew his name-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mayor [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the mayor of Haifa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was the right hand, Schmuel Bialig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we played soccer but we didn't other towns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was mostly more involved in the scouts and the Hanoar Hatzioni, which was the center Zionists.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the children were called Hanoar, which means the youth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would go to the-- you know, you would have uniforms and would go for these so-called wars, where you tag-- you tag your enemy and you win his tie.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- And it so happened that in 1939, on August 30 when we came out from one of these excursions, we saw a sign on the wall, mobilization.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were so happy we were going to see a real war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we did see a real war, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the very next morning, we had dead people in our-- in our city.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
